#: ../../../system/ppc/powernv.rst:61
msgid ""
"KVM acceleration in Linux Power hosts is provided by the kvm-hv and kvm-pr "
"modules. kvm-hv is adherent to PAPR and it's not compliant with powernv. kvm-"
"pr in theory could be used as a valid accel option but this isn't supported "
"by kvm-pr at this moment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/ppc/powernv.rst:66
